{"tid":91718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙祠首設頭炷香倒數","createTime":"2017-01-23T05:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T14:17:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3fc3aa4d4846827a6bac794303680b9d32c4009","tid":91718,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170122/19905120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170122%2F19905120&d=ihKXy5AFm8UklAqt1nq4ZRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=0fa692be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170122%2F19905120&h=ed3dc2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170122/19905120</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】每年年卅晚均有大批善信湧至黃大仙祠爭上頭炷香，今年祠方有新安排，首設倒數頭炷香環節，還將公眾香爐移近大殿6呎，讓善信近距離參拜黃大仙。祠方又新增了頭炷香限定活動，包括緣在月老、迎春接福發鼓三通等，祈願新年幸福美滿。<br />\n減煙系統除懸浮粒子<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙祠發言人稱，自家研發的電子簽文機將於新春後首次開放給公眾，屆時善信可以自助領取簽文；亦研發了全港首個廟宇「煙香減少及除味系統」，放置大殿前，昨日正式啟用，去除懸浮粒子的效能達80%或以上，去除甲醛及氣味均高於60%；並配合香灰再生計劃，將大量香灰經化學處理，把鹼、硅、鋁等元素混合、加壓及加熱等，變為特定的沸石形態，再經過濾、清洗及風乾，製成成除臭吸味顆粒。<br />\n發言人續指園內分別在大殿、三聖堂及盂香亭設乾式及濕式環保化香爐，減少煙塵。<br />\n■記者蔡朗清"},{"pid":"8901ca5a31797cf950ebde735ba3fc6c824cf1d4","tid":91718,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"今年夏威夷扮雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeee1ae3febab60e6b36a58552174d295ad30333","tid":91718,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"夏蕙BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddafb2395bb26f175f66c9f9ee28ee4d5803fac","tid":91718,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab3b218001dd45b584f31bbd9798efdde51ea8f","tid":91718,"uid":31017,"like":0,